caption.title: Compare to mosquitoes fed with 0ng/ml ivermectin, the reduction degree of maximum, median, P 75, P 25 of DENV-2 RNA concentration for each treatment group.
caption.p: The calculation formula is as follows: (parameter (e.g. median) in mosquitoes fed with 0ng/ml ivermectin-parameter in each treatment group)/ parameter in mosquitoes fed with 0ng/ml ivermectin*100%.
